    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Medium-sized or small hand tools for breaking up rocks, usually having a flat head with either a chisel or a pick head at the other end, made of steel or other metal, mounted on a handle.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
